| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-5425 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: ae7c39ef-b8da-5a96-9b92-c03e41dadb9c"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
